{intro}Allows for a visual break in your wiki content.{intro}

{section:Example}
*Source Markup*
{{
top content
----
bottom content
}}

{p}*Rendered Markup*{p}
{p}
top content
{markup}<hr />{markup}
bottom content
{p}

{alert:note}
The horizontal rule must be the first thing on a line. Content can follow it, but when rendered - will render on a new line.
{alert}
